{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Single-cell DNA sequencing has been performed on previously characterized organoids 14.",
    "Organoids from passage 4 and passage 15 were frozen in Recovery Cell Culture Freezing Medium (Thermo #12648010) and processed at BCCRC as described 30.",
    "Briefly, samples were gently thawed, and single cells were isolated from frozen organoid suspension using Trypsin treatment.",
    "Single cells were spotted using a cellenONE (Scienion) instrument.",
    "Subsequently, libraries were constructed using previously described protocol 30 and approximately 1000 cells were sequenced on an Illumina HiSeq 2500 instrument."
  ],
